These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
House: art-deco, townhouse, modern, craftsman
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, baseball, parkour, cricket
4 different games are played: backgammon, bridge, whist, poker
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, australian, polish, argentine
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the australian##3
 2. the townhouse house is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 3. the thai is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the polish is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 5. the thai is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 7. the modern house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 8. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 9. the thai is on the far left##1
10. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
11. the person playing bridge is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| House    | modern   | townhouse       | art-deco | craftsman   |
| Sport        | baseball    | cricket  | parkour      | rowing |
| Game         | poker      | bridge | whist         | backgammon   |
| Nationality   | thai | australian       | polish        | argentine   |

