.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower, dahlia, daisy
City: venice, new-york, liverpool, boston
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, asparagus, pomegranate, lemon
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, old-henry, vegafina, bluemaster
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person traveling to venice##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is between the person traveling to new-york and the cain-smoker##2
5. the cain-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
6. the person eating lemon is the bluemaster-smoker##1
7. the person eating grapefruit is on the far right##1
8. the cain-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Flower           | balloon-flower | bellflower | daisy | dahlia |
| City   | venice  | liverpool | new-york         | boston      |
| Food         | pomegranate      | asparagus    | lemon         | grapefruit   |
| Cigar     | cain         | old-henry    | bluemaster          | vegafina         |

