.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, german, chinese, nigerian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, mirinda, soy-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, zombie, epic, spy
City: miami, rome, paris, hamburg
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the chinese##1
 2. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
 4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
 7. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 8. the person watching disaster movies is between the person traveling to paris and the person drinking lemonade##2
 9. the nigerian is on the left of the mexican##1
10. the german is on the left or right of the nigerian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Nationality          | german | nigerian  | mexican | chinese      |
| Beverage   | tea       | soy-milk    | lemonade      | mirinda      |
| Movie-Genre           | spy     | disaster     | zombie         | epic   |
| City         | paris | miami | rome     | hamburg |

