 4. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
 5. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
 7. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
 8. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 9. the dunhill-smoker is the person eating corn##1
10. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |     4     |
| Flower         | sunflower      | orchid | dahlia       | azalea   |
| Pet   | guinea-pig     | frog | bird | horse |
| Food   | nectarine    | cherry     | orange        | corn       |
| Cigar     | tiparillo | dannemann   | havana   | dunhill       |

