.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, montecristo, havana, siglo
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, mauve, blood-red, grey
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, tulip, marigold, aconite
City: edinburgh, london, rome, marseilles
 1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far right##1
 2. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 3. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
 4. the person who likes mauve is between the person traveling to rome and the person traveling to london##2
 5. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
 6. the person who growsorchid is between the person who likes mauve and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
 7. the person who growsmarigold is the person who likes grey##1
 8. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 9. the havana-smoker is the person who likes mauve##1
10. the person who growsorchid is the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Cigar          | montecristo | siglo   | havana   | bluemaster |
| Color           | lavender   | blood-red     | mauve   | grey |
| Flower   | tulip    | orchid    | aconite   | marigold   |
| City         | edinburgh    | london | marseilles | rome    |

 